Class StudentView

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Scene
      • view.ViewGeneric
        • view.StudentView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Subject, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class StudentView
extends ViewGeneric
    This class extends ViewGeneric which is used as a switch for showing different scenes This class produces the view that the student see when they login.
